Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I spent my summer at a \Nplace in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I beat up some cutesy couples \Nat the tennis court,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Fought some grade schoolers over who
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,would get their radio exercises \Ncard stamped first,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:23.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,caught more stag beetles \Nthan I really should have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I had good time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I really would have liked \Nit if you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kyun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:42.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Kyun! Kyun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:42.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:52.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hatate-kun, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:56.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I was sad, not being able \Nto see you for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:09.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?!
