Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:44.01,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(770,1)}Hold This {\c&HD0C260&}for Me. \N{\c&H984FD9&}The Winner {\c&H65BC94&}of the {\c&HA760E2&}Beauty Contest {\c&H25ABF1&}is Written {\c&HCFC063&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:51.98,new_friend_02:46,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,New friend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:50.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have a new friend for you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Clap, clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the Principality of Bladefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:03:00.49,Hakua_02:53,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,1)}Hakua B. Bladefield
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,the second crown princess, \NHakua Berserker Bladefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's more of a princess than Knight-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I want to protect \Nher more than Knight-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,She smells better than Knight-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real princess, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be starting the new term today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,The school fair's coming up,\Nso make sure you all behave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,along with your new friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We just got off of summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and now everyone's excited \Nabout the school fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the largest festival around here. \NIt lasts for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone from the elementary school \Ndivision to the university here participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:55.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,My class wants to make their \Nhaunted yakisoba café a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,so they're all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:04:00.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of chemical reaction created that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua-chan has gotten really used to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:13.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always watch after her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,please sign this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't marriage paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:26.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I... I would be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,just to be your lover, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.83,lover_04:29,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Lover
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be an {\i1}annoying{\i0} way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't mind signing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's an entry sheet for the \NHatagaya Academy beauty contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya beauty contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the main attractions \Nfor the first day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said that if you put their name in,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,they wouldn't mind entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.57,entry_05:02,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.57,Name_05:02,,0000,0000,0000,,Name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.57,Black_name_05:02,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahougasawa Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:09.70,contest_05:02,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hatagaya Academy Beauty Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mahougasawa Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.32,entry_05:05,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.32,Name_05:05,,0000,0000,0000,,Name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.32,Black_name_05:02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H35333D&}Shoukanji Kikuno
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Shoukanji Kikuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.70,entry_05:05,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.70,Name_05:05,,0000,0000,0000,,Name
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.70,Black_name_05:07,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami K. Bladefield
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami Knight Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri and Mei, Hakua and Rin-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The president and Megumu are here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:24.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are nice, little Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of someone putting in a word
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,for nine girls at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,How unscrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,he wanted you to enter, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:44.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to get happy \Nover something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You get so embarrassed. It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,So, since you nominated them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to need to \Ntreat them all equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My class is supposed to help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is the school fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have fun with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun with everyone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:22.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Japan likes \Nmaids so much, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:23.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You two look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a perfectly manly maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:36.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:40.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lower my head for you, even if I am
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,the second crown princess, Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.01,social_status_06:43,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Social status
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Dealing with social status is annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about getting \Nready for the beauty contest, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't interested in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let me enter you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't allowed myself to be entered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,everyone would think I wasn't \Nbeing friendly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:07.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:10.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:14.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is the poster for the \Nbeauty contest, so smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're always smiling, and now you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I'm some \Nsort of smiling expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I look gloomy all the time, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be comparing yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How about you try taking the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take your picture, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've been in \Na room without anyone else around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's trying their best \Nfor this fair business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't enjoy myself, Granny-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get that fairy tale out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.10,social_status_06:43,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,To Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I found some stuff I thought were clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everything would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much fun I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that boy that was the flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Your door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:49.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worrying about something \Non your own again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's already so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'd be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll get a late \Nnight snack or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should get some \Npeople together to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What about you guys? Okiku-nee, Hakua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:38.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, Hakua's here, so I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a special thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,A sister is only supposed to let her \Nbrother sleep on her lap like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,A sister doesn't need any little sisters \Nother than her younger brother's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You know, she is my little \Nsister, not his, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm charging, so I cannot go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you guys, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:13.00,Maid_10:07,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, school at night is kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:34.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like we're fairies that \Nhave wandered into another land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:37.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice poem, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say poem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It went "kyuu."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Your cute stomach went "kyuu."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No. It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sound that plays when \NI get a text from my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, it said "kyuu, kyuu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu, kyuu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:08.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu, kyuu, kyuu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu, kyuu, kyuu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu... Kyuu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, too, Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:21.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyuu... Kyuu... Kyuu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Nanami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone so excited \Nthe night before the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:46.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, why was that so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You only thought of that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I guess \NMegu thought that was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:18.72,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:23.31,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to be \Nhappy while they can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,So it's time to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,start the Hatagaya Academy school fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,And we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We get a week long school fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,And the opening event \Nthat everyone must see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.40,contest_12:39,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hatagaya Academy Beauty Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Miss Hatagaya Academy beauty contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your host, the ace \Nof the broadcast team,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Kondawara Fuu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:51.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,and... Me, Nonomiya Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Time to introduce our judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:57.17,Tsumugi_12:54,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,250)}Ryuukishibara \NTsumugi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We have a legendary guest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,She once won 10 contests in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuukishibara Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,If only I were 50 years younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We have our representative from \Nthe middle school division:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:08.10,Tsumugi_12:54,,0000,0000,0000,,Daishikyougawa \NKurumiko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Daishikyougawa Kurumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Get your ice cream here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,And last we have the person who \Nsponsored all of our entrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.02,Tsumugi_12:54,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,250)}Hatate \NSouta
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making me judge this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,You had all them do this \Nand you're saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:26.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,And all of our participants \Nare from Quest Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,If he knows them all personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,he can keep any problems between\Nthem from getting out of hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:37.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(78,8)}So much for doing what you're supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.30,swimsuit_15:09,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hatagaya Academy Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Our first entry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.05,swimsuit_15:09,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Entry #1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Mahougasawa Akane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mahougasawa Akane-san here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I like Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Eiyuuzaki Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I-I also like Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... What are you making me say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Shoukanji Kikuno here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I love my little brother and \Nthe guy close to my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and they're both Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:11.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souta-kyu— I mean Hatate-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Is going to make me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.24,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Peek, peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:14.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me so much, Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:18.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:20.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ninjabayashi Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I am belongs to Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That's supposed to be for the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy just having met Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:41.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I could happily die right now, I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why so serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do the best I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:48.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the bonds we have together,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,that surpass normal manly friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not really sure why I'm here. \NGuess it's a bit late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, but I'm \Nsure it's Souta's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:00.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's all nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll have our audience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,vote in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,First is our swimsuit competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.38,swimsuit_15:09,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuit Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is supposed to be a \Nswimsuit competition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,hiding their swimsuit with a shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,So what happens when we have Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,stand over there with a water gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,I know now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a wet t-shirt \Nplus swimsuit competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty perverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what we like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Now go at it, Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so bothered, Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:48.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, spray it all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun, don't get so much on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:07.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want lots on me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Spray it all over me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:23.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I want more, Hatate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I want some, too, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you my upgraded \Nwaterproof features.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:45.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything for you Souta-san, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you getting a little too much on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting it on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:11.11,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that brings our swimsuit \Ncompetition to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:19.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone has the same amount \Nof votes from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,And if we add in the votes from our judges...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,We got the same amount votes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get it right, judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't rate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:39.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to add another \Ncompetition to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Our final competition is an
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.54,swimsuit_15:09,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Ardently Confess Your Love to the Judges
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,"ardently confess your love \Nto the judges" competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You think the audience is going to like
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,that in a beauty competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,They've all seen just how much
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,these girls are trying to impress Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya Academy is all about \Nwishing the best for these girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:02.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,even if you don't get them yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Knight-san, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:11.57,poem_18:06,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(105,1)}Poem fight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm a little less nervous now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't like you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It started when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You were a wimp, hated yourself, \Nand were always so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were carrying the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,misfortune of the entire world on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And well, I guess a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had seen you \Ncrack a smile or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but now you're back to your old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should just
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,headbutt you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you're thinking \Nabout it in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:24.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for hanging in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like something \Nchanged because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.82,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My fate and the death flag were still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.61,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But someone noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.69,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.50,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,that'd make me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Was my confession of love that boring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You care about him so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It just touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left for us to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You won, Princess Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,You made use of your differing \Nattitudes for that speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:19.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I detected a "tsundere level" of 530,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Today Nanami's Sou-kun's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Points for Knight-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,She broke through the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,She might as well have won already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:32.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,No complaints here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.67,swimsuit_15:09,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,So that makes Nanami Knight \NBladefield-san the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nanami-chan, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:40.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What is this even?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Knight-san's victory she wins the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,right to a date with Souta-kun \Nfor the school fair
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,and a free pass to the refreshment stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.06,souta_20:54,Yoshiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You've been eating quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I'm going to have the most fun I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:12.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you made me say all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:12.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Please hide me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:20.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:12.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to come into the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:15.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was finally time for me to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:20.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could you say that a bit louder?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:22.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,My turn to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:24.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't hear you. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:28.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Blah! Why aren't you going to introduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:32.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but there's no flag to spoil \Nwhat's going to happen next episode.
